  This Arc file contains the following programs:
 
 
          Display.bas
             This is the Picture Displayer program. It Run s in Low
          Resolution, but it will display both Low Res Neochrome and
          and low and Medium Resolution Degas Picture s. The program
          has basically 2 modes of Operation.
 
               Mode 1:
                  Display all Picture Files on a disk until you press
               and Hold Both Mouse Button's down.
 
               Mode 2:
                  Use of script files which will display only those
               Files contain within a Script file until you press and
               hold both Mouse button's down.
 
 
 
 
          Scriptbl.Bas
              This is the script Builder File Maker Program. It will
          It will build Script Files for you. Read the instruction s
          display when run.
 
 
 
   These program's have been a real learning experience for me. Thank's
